  <brief_title>Dose-dependent Effect of Fentanyl on Cough Attenuation During Emergence From General Anaesthesia</brief_title>
  <official_title>Dose-dependent Effect of Fentanyl on Cough Attenuation During Emergence From General Anaesthesia</official_title>
